OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FTyson Fury is set to return to the
OL,7,Fring on Saturday, where he is facing
OL,8,Fthe Russian bear-fighting Arslanbek
OL,9,FMakhmudov.
OL,11,FIt will be Fury's first fight since
OL,12,Fhis second defeat to Oleksandr Usyk in
OL,13,FDecember 2024, after which he
OL,14,Fannounced his retirement before
OL,15,Fconfirming in January this year that
OL,16,Fhe would return to the ring.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
