OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F312A1775865772
OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FDespite his hiatus, Fury remains one
OL,7,Fof the biggest names in the sport, and
OL,8,Fa victory would intensify the long-
OL,9,Frunning conversation about a showdown
OL,10,Fwith fellow Brit, Anthony Joshua.
OL,12,FFury said he wants to fight Joshua,
OL,13,Fand in the pre-match interviews for
OL,14,FSaturday's fight, floated a possible
OL,15,FSeptember date - though nothing has
OL,16,Fbeen confirmed.
OL,18,FBut first, Fury said: "I'm going to
OL,19,Fconcentrate on this big Russian fella."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
