OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FITV News breaks down everything you
OL,7,Fneed to know about Saturday's fight.
OL,9,FWho is Arslanbek Makhmudov?
OL,11,FMakhmudov, 36, is a Russian national
OL,12,Fwho currently lives in Canada and
OL,13,Fholds a 21-2 record in the ring.
OL,15,FHis most recent fight was a 12-round
OL,16,Funanimous decision over Dave Allen in
OL,17,FOctober.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
