OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FMakhmudov's left eye was swollen shut
OL,7,Fin a loss to Guido Vianello in 2024.
OL,8,FHe was felled by Agit Kabayel's body
OL,9,Fshots in a fourth-round stoppage in
OL,10,F2023.
OL,12,FIn the run-up to the fight, Makhmudov,
OL,13,Fshared a video of him sparring with a
OL,14,Fbear, saying: "The goal was to
OL,15,Fovercome the threshold of fear and
OL,16,Flearn to control yourself in critical
OL,17,Fsituations."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
