OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FMakhmudov told the Guardian he
OL,7,Fbelieved Fury was one of the sport's
OL,8,Fall-time greats, but he believed he
OL,9,Fwould win.
OL,11,FHe said: "Tyson Fury is the professor
OL,12,Fof mind and boxing. A lot of boxing is
OL,13,Fmental and he is a master. But boxing
OL,14,Fis also spiritual. I am going to be
OL,15,Fstrong, spiritual and smart.
OL,17,F"You can say this is a war between
OL,18,Fmental and spiritual, and we'll see
OL,19,Fwho is more successful. Inshallah, it
OL,20,Fis spiritual."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
