OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FFury is also not taking Makhmudov
OL,7,Flying down, telling reporters on
OL,8,FThursday: "I've never overlooked
OL,9,Fanybody in my life, and I'll
OL,10,Fdefinitely not overlook this beast.
OL,11,FHe's a scary dude."
OL,13,FWhat about Fury's future?
OL,15,FFury has stated he isn't just coming
OL,16,Fout of retirement to fight Makhmudov,
OL,17,Fand has outlined a plan for three
OL,18,Ffights this year.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
