OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FTelling reporters in the run-up to
OL,7,FSaturday's match, he said he wanted to
OL,8,Ffight Joshua in September and
OL,9,Fpotentially a third attempt to beat
OL,10,Fworld champion Usyk.
OL,12,FA fight between Fury and Joshua has
OL,13,Flong been planned but never
OL,14,Fmaterialised. With both in and out of
OL,15,Fretirement, it has looked increasingly
OL,16,Funlikely in recent years.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
