OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FFury told reporters on Friday: "This
OL,7,Ffight was supposed to happen so many
OL,8,Ftimes over the last 10 years, but then
OL,9,Fsomeone has had one more fight in
OL,10,Fbetween and someone has got knocked
OL,11,Fout or injured.
OL,13,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,14,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,15,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,16,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,18,F"I think we should get this fight on
OL,19,Fas soon as possible in case something
OL,20,Fhappens in between.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
