OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,F"The problem is that in heavyweight
OL,7,Fboxing, anything can go wrong, there
OL,8,Fare no easy fights. And if you get
OL,9,Fknocked upside down, it's finished,
OL,10,Fit's done. I want it as the fight
OL,11,Fnext, and I'm sure AJ feels the same."
OL,13,FThe 36-year-old Joshua called out Fury
OL,14,Fafter breaking Jake Paul's jaw in a
OL,15,Fstoppage victory in December.
OL,17,FBut just a few days later, Joshua was
OL,18,Finvolved in a fatal car crash in
OL,19,FNigeria, throwing his future into
OL,20,Fdoubt.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
