OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FHe was a passenger in the vehicle, and
OL,7,Ftwo of his close friends were killed.
OL,8,FThe driver of the car, Adeniyi
OL,9,FMobolaji Kayode, has been charged in
OL,10,Frelation to the crash.
OL,12,FBut it appears Joshua is set to resume
OL,13,Ffighting. He has returned to training
OL,14,Fand was seen last weekend attending
OL,15,Fthe Deontay Wilder vs Derek Chisora
OL,16,Fbout in London.
OL,18,FWhen and where is the fight?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
