OL,3,C'He's a scary dude': When and where
OL,4,Ccan you watch Fury vs Makhmudov?
OL,6,FThe fight is taking place on Saturday
OL,7,Fat the Tottenham Hotspur Stadium. It
OL,8,Fwill be Fury's first fight in the UK
OL,9,Fsince 2022.
OL,11,FThe main card begins at 7pm and is
OL,12,Favailable on Netflix.
OL,14,FFury's ring walk is expected around
OL,15,F10.30pm, about one hour after Conor
OL,16,FBenn vs Regis Prograis.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
